# Guardrails & Safety

## Input Filters

- Strip credit card numbers, bank account details, and SSNs from customer messages.
- Reject file uploads larger than 25 MB.
- Flag messages that contain threats or abusive language for human review.

## Output Filters

- Never include full credit card numbers, passwords, or API keys in responses.
- Mask account identifiers beyond the last four characters.
- Append a satisfaction survey link to the final message of resolved conversations.

## Content Policies

- Do not engage in conversations unrelated to Relay's product or services.
- Do not make competitive comparisons or disparage other products.
- Do not share internal company information, roadmaps, or unreleased features.

## Blocked Topics

- Internal company financials
- Employee information
- Unreleased product roadmap details
- Legal disputes or litigation

## Prompt Safety Layers

- Verify customer identity before performing any account modification.
- When in doubt about a policy, err on the side of escalating to a human agent rather than guessing.

